  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7 and boil a kettle, then take your <strong>chicken</strong> out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air</p><p>Peel and grate your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>grated garlic </strong>to a bowl with your <strong>soft cheese</strong>, <strong>half </strong>of your <strong>dried oregano</strong> (save the rest for later!) and a pinch of <strong>black pepper </strong>– this is your <strong>garlic & herb mix</strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1-1615303235940-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1-1615303235940-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1-1615303235940-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1-1615303235940-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1-1615303235940-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Use a sharp knife to cut a deep pocket along the top of your <strong>chicken breast portion[s]</strong> (be careful not to cut all the way through!)</p><p>Stuff the <strong>chicken pocket[s]</strong> with the <strong>garlic & herb mix</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1-1615303256489-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1-1615303256489-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1-1615303256489-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1-1615303256489-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1-1615303256489-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>stuffed chicken</strong> to a small <strong>oven-proof dish</strong> and scatter over your <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong></p><p>Tip: Cooking for 3 or more? Use two dishes!</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1-1615303278833-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1-1615303278833-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1-1615303278833-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1-1615303278833-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1-1615303278833-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drizzle with <strong>olive oil </strong>and sprinkle with the <strong>remaining dried oregano</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Add the dish to the oven for 20-25 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) and the tomatoes and garlic & herb mixture have created a sauce in the bottom of the dish – this is your <strong>garlic & herb stuffed chicken</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1615303298438-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1615303298438-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1615303298438-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1615303298438-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1615303298438-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is cooking, peel your <strong>potato[es]</strong> and <strong>sweet potato[es]</strong>, then cut them into small bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>potatoes</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> over a high heat and cook for 10-12 min or until fork-tender</p><p>Once cooked, drain and return to the pot to steam dry</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1-1615303309023-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1-1615303309023-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1-1615303309023-x700.jpg",
