            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Trim, then add your <strong>green beans</strong> to a baking tray (or two!) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Once the chicken has 10 min left, add the tray[s] to the oven and cook for 8-10 min until the beans have softened and started to brown – these are your <strong>roasted green beans</strong></p>",
